lead_paragraph: Ryan Murphy won the men's 100 meters backstroke gold at the Rio Olympics on Monday to extend United States swimmers' run of domination in the event to six successive Games dating back to Atlanta in 1996.

headline.print_headline: Murphy Maintains U.S. Streak in 100m Backstroke
